\par
\pard\b Table 2 Difference in Mean Attendance Outcomes\b0\par
\par
\pard Outcome 	 JMTES mean 	 JES mean 	 Difference\par
\pard Unexcused absence % 	 5.444 	 9.009 	 -3.564\par
